         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#444]"> Intellectual Property Rights (IPR) relate to creations of the mind — including inventions, designs, written or artistic work, brand names, logos, software, and other original content used in business or creative activity. Proper protection gives the owner legal control over how such assets are used. </p>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#444] mt-2"> Registering and managing intellectual property helps prevent unauthorized use and also allows businesses to generate value through licensing, assignment, franchising, or partnerships. Strong IP protection often improves credibility with investors and strengthens brand position in the market. </p>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#444] mt-2"> At 
            <strong>Legalx24</strong>, we assist startups, founders, creators, and established companies in identifying, registering, and enforcing their intellectual property rights through practical legal strategies suited to their business needs. </p>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#444] mt-2"> Our support covers the full lifecycle of intellectual property — from initial search and registration to portfolio management, enforcement, dispute handling, and guidance on international protection where required. </p>
